name: roland nills
description:
Am Attractive, passionate, sensual, romantic, intelligent, young at heart, happy, fun, affectionate, easy-going, have a good sense of humour, active and independent. I’m comfortable in myself as much as socializing and meeting people. Honest, tender, responsible and need the same back, quiet yet still full of life. I value friendship in a relationship, have experience to know whats important. Have a good enough material life and like the finer things in life, have a passion making music especially Jazz. Love to stroll around musea and art galleries.
I don’t smoke, don’t drink, don’t do drugs.
